    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/8d76b6f113dec3057c941580dbea3367.avif?t=1760650003\" width=1200 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“一个从孤独、债务和肮脏中诞生的成功故事。”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的妻子离开了你。你失去了家。你的生活崩溃了。</strong><br><strong>就在你以为一切都结束时……一张传单砸到了你的头上：</strong><br><strong>“廉价出租：旧汽车站厕所”</strong><br><strong>于是，《厕所模拟器》的故事就此开始。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/d40e54a7fc979616eb0ca3bec4c6dea7.poster.avif?t=1760650003\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/d40e54a7fc979616eb0ca3bec4c6dea7.webm?t=1760650003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/d40e54a7fc979616eb0ca3bec4c6dea7.mp4?t=1760650003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/353558fb9525485bde91b85d2210b6af.poster.avif?t=1760650003\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/353558fb9525485bde91b85d2210b6af.webm?t=1760650003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/353558fb9525485bde91b85d2210b6af.mp4?t=1760650003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/40f0137e4bb4f6d7ebfbb1bc51a96c00.webp?t=1760650003\" width=519 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>接管一座破旧、被遗弃的公共厕所，把它打造成全城最具代表性的卫生圣地。</strong><br><strong>清理、装饰、选择马桶，甚至摆放肥皂分配器。</strong><br><strong>但请注意：这仅仅是个开始。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/e80d3d95b44236ddec365a9c6425c151.webp?t=1760650003\" width=401 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/7c3a3eb01ffb47e3d47ddbbdcb6a9eb3.poster.avif?t=1760650003\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/7c3a3eb01ffb47e3d47ddbbdcb6a9eb3.webm?t=1760650003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/7c3a3eb01ffb47e3d47ddbbdcb6a9eb3.mp4?t=1760650003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抵御变态、窃贼和黑手党</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集垃圾、修理损坏的物品并购买清洁用品</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>让顾客满意——否则他们将永远不会再来</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自行设定厕所使用费用</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>吃饭、购物或喝一杯放松一下——一切都在终点站中可用！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314740/extras/6d6e7efcd6c6e29328cfd723d8235b1f.webp?t=1760650003\" width=336 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在试玩版中，你只能完成教程任务。</strong><br><strong>在抢先体验版中，你将解锁所有其他任务和更多内容。</strong><br><strong>完成试玩任务后，你将学会核心玩法机制，并为完整游戏做好准备。</strong></p>",
